Class DefaultGenerationConfig

java.lang.Object
org.jsonschema2pojo.DefaultGenerationConfig
All Implemented Interfaces:
GenerationConfig
public class DefaultGenerationConfig extends Object implements GenerationConfig
A generation config that returns default values for all behavioural options.
